name: MSRI-ONE-GIFOBY-Wh-01
description: v4w.enko - "MSRI-ONE-GIFOBY-Wh-01" Is a single perspective projection artwork. Gif animation of one 3d Object is  generated from custom definition. 2 lofts are animated in 2 layers for each color: Orange and  Blue. The cells of the Yellow "3d voronoi" cube are linked to the attractor`s points of the lofts. Another one group of cells of the white cube is rotating. The perspective view is drawing maximum details in the resolution of  1024*1024 pixels. Total 128 frames, 1024*1024px canvas.
